Reliance Understands India  #Yousta is a new fashion brand launched by #Reliance Retail in India on August 24, 2023. It promises to offer all products under â‚¹999, with most of them priced under â‚¹499. Yousta is aimed at the youth (15-25 years) and offers apparel, footwear, fashion accessories, beauty products, and much more for boys, girls, men, and women.  Here are some facts about Yousta fashion brand:  It is a youth-focused brand that promises affordable fashion shopping.  All products are priced below â‚¹999, while most of them are under â‚¹499.  Yousta offers apparel, footwear, fashion accessories, beauty products, and much more.  It is a tech-savvy brand with QR-enabled screens, self-checkout counters, complimentary Wi-Fi and charging stations.  The company plans to open at least 200 stores across India by the end of this financial year.  Yousta is a new brand, so it remains to be seen how it will be received by the Indian market. However, it has the potential to be a popular choice for young people looking for affordable fashion.
